# Yarn Classic config for the dashboard.
# ignore-engines: a transitive dev dep (eslint-visitor-keys@5) declares node
# ^20.19 || ^22.13 || >=24; we run node 22.12, a trivial patch behind. The package
# works fine on 22.12, so don't fail `yarn install` over it (saves passing
# --ignore-engines by hand every time). To drop this, move to node >= 22.13.
--ignore-engines true
